# Frontend Build Check

After modifying any `.ts` or `.vue` file under `3rd/CoralinkerHost/ClientApp/`, run the TypeScript type check to verify there are no compile errors:

```bash
cd 3rd/CoralinkerHost/ClientApp && npx vue-tsc --noEmit
```

Fix all type errors before considering the task complete.
